high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the counter to the right of the sink
Pick up the light brown bowl that is on the right of the plant
Turn around and walk to the fridge on your left

Open the fridge and place the bowl on the bottom shelf to the left of the lettuce then close the fridge.  Open the fridge and pick up the bowl that is sitting to the left of the lettuce then close the fridge
Turn around and walk to the sink that is to your right
Place the bowl in the sink to the right
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled bowl in a sink

high_descs: Turn to your right to face the counter to right of the sink
Pick up the bowl from the counter
Open the fridge, put the bowl on the tray with the cabbage, close the fridge, wait a few seconds and take the bowl out of the fridge
Put the bowl in the sink
anns.task_desc: Place the chilled bowl in the sink

high_descs: Turn around and face the counter on the left.
Pick up the orange cup from the back of the counter.
Carry the cup and turn around. Face the fridge on the left.
Open the fridge and place the cup inside. Shut the door and then open it. Take out the cup and shut the door.
Carry the cup and turn to the left. Turn left again and face the sink on the right.
Place the cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Chill a cup and place it in the sink.
